{"tid":2321400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指定檢疫酒店名單大揭秘　駿洋邨成犧牲品！！！","createTime":"2020-12-11T12:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T14:26:13.000Z","uid":244704,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"625b909e31bbd7de8d37c03992c49e88965101db","tid":2321400,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"指定檢疫酒店名單大揭秘 駿洋邨成犧牲品！！！<br />\n<br />\n拫據「指定檢疫酒店名單」發現距離機場最近的兩間酒店分別是<br />\n【香港東涌福朋喜來登酒店】同【 富豪機場酒店】這兩間酒店可提供（非套房及套房）總共有２１６４個房間，若連同【香港天際萬豪酒店】成指定檢疫酒店則共有２８２２個房間，這三間酒店房間總數是駿洋邨的單位數目五成以上，事實上疫情初期根本毋須借用駿洋邨成檢疫中心，是政府在疫情初期不把武肺病毒放在眼內，並把市民生命放上刑台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「指定檢疫酒店名單」<a href=\"https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/designated-hotel-list_tc.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coronavirus.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdesignated-hotel-list_tc.pdf&d=gjdgNhcllSDI%2FgTZdT0hmoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=3a6b3a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.coronavirus.gov.hk/pdf/designated-hotel-list_tc.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"2b09d55438e86f947622c6bbd2b7496c63b08337","tid":2321400,"uid":76804,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/blogger/2020/06/%E6%9A%89%E6%98%8E%E9%82%A8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fblogger%2F2020%2F06%2F%25E6%259A%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E9%2582%25A8.jpg&h=eb5c2f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200127/s00006/dfd84985912f577d29503ac0ea0f4cc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200127%2Fs00006%2Fdfd84985912f577d29503ac0ea0f4cc1.jpg&h=99eaed49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20200127/s00006/dfd873e6d86b05a672f0136bf7b9dc71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20200127%2Fs00006%2Fdfd873e6d86b05a672f0136bf7b9dc71.jp